Plague Cloud	KEY:Plague Cloud ~ Virulent Zombie		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Supernatural		DEFINE:PlagueCloudDC|0	DESC:As a standard action, a virulent zombie can unleash a cloud of disease. Treat this as a Fog Cloud (CL %1), but any creature in the area at the start of its turn must make a Fortitude saving throw or risk contracting zombie rot. This cloud travels in a straight line away from the zombie at a speed of 10 feet per round and it dissipates after 1d6 rounds. Once a virulent zombie has used this ability, it must wait 1d4 rounds before using it again. Zombie Rot-cloud; save Fort DC %2; onset 1d4 days; frequency 1 day; effect 1d2 Con damage; cure 2 consecutive saves. Anyone who dies while infected rises as a plague zombie in 2d6 hours.|HD|PlagueCloudDC	BONUS:VAR|PlagueCloudDC|10+(HD/2)+CHA+2	SOURCEPAGE:p.5

